= SDL_CondWait =
Use this function to wait on the condition variable, unlocking the provided mutex.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_CondWait(SDL_cond*  cond,
                 SDL_mutex* mut)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''cond'''
|^a pointer to the SDL_cond structure that is being applied^ ???
